{"tid":1551072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人話收到咁嘅message，話警察比人抹黑，阿媽叫個女「為國捐軀」","createTime":"2019-09-07T22:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T23:06:22.000Z","uid":50275,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d79318b09a4fbe9e22c3c9bd244e1bb63099fcdf","tid":1551072,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:34:18.000Z","msg":"我今年11歲，自細阿媽就教我愛中國，同我講我流嘅係中國人嘅血，國家有難，我地炎黃子孫一定要幫手。六月開始有好多暴徒攻擊國家、襲擊警察，大家都知道警察好辛苦。七月二日，暴徒攻擊立法會之後，阿媽買左件靚裙比我，叫我著住條裙同佢出去。<br />\n<br />\n我地屋企係沙田區，個日我地坐巴士出去，記得好多男人望住我，令我好唔自然，可能我試過著咁少布嘅衫。無幾耐，我地去到九龍某一區，係一條內街，有個大叔同阿媽打招呼「辛苦你們，為了國家」，我覺得大叔好面善但又醒唔起係邊度見過佢⋯⋯跟住佢就帶我地係度鐵門入去，一入度去，發現遠處幾個藍色制服嘅人，我呆左，好似係警署？<br />\n<br />\n我好驚，好緊張，究竟我係咪犯左咩錯⋯⋯我一路跟住佢地行一路震，去到一樓，有一間房門口，大叔停低左⋯⋯「李sir」有一個著藍色制服嘅人叫佢，然後幫佢開門⋯⋯一入去，入面坐住十零個女仔，好似同我差唔多年紀，阿媽叫我唔使驚，聽正義既警察叔叔講，記住：「我地會為國捐軀」<br />\n<br />\n我就入去坐低左。無幾耐，有十幾個男人入黎，「你地愛國嘅就除衫，為國捐軀」，在場其他女仔開始唱國歌「起來⋯⋯」之後開始除衫⋯⋯我唔知點算⋯⋯我驚人話我唔愛國⋯⋯我就跟住佢地做⋯⋯之後佢地輪住搞啲女仔⋯⋯我驚人話我唔愛國⋯⋯我就跟住做⋯⋯我愛國所以我捐軀⋯⋯我愛國⋯⋯我一路喊自己一路諗住我愛中國⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=20028912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D20028912&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=e7044b50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=20028912</a>"},{"pid":"493f532e463f0a5f75dac0110e3ff99f23902f1f","tid":1551072,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「為國捐軀？」"},{"pid":"33510425aabea45971c0e0960376ac101d68825d","tid":1551072,"uid":261819,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:36:29.000Z","msg":"我到底睇左d 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468c3345e4f28b778568b07f0681de26f4336a03","tid":1551072,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:39:18.000Z","msg":"個故仔作到咁, 應該好快沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cbf4589e832b7ac794569b419041ac9ed54e8d","tid":1551072,"uid":52596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:51:34.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2191aa24a8f56a48dbcbd0c0a12978106f47754","tid":1551072,"uid":2290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:59:03.000Z","msg":"有智商嘅人都知假到on9啦，你又走黎share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275c40cf52a91f51d6623c061032c6adb2bd326e","tid":1551072,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:00:13.000Z","msg":"share鬼文=鬼<br />\n<br />\n次次都係用返呢句 :<br />\n藍絲朋友send比我點駁"},{"pid":"3b86fd5a5b3ecd9e344a83a9d01eaffa3e889e75","tid":1551072,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468c3345e4f28b778568b07f0681de26f4336a03","tid":1551072,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:39:18.000Z","msg":"個故仔作到咁, 應該好快沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"應該係比喻<br />\n不過作得差<br />\n難入口"},{"pid":"88e8e0c9cc6bbb367604e79110f1f0c8f139edd0","tid":1551072,"uid":193538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:02:06.000Z","msg":"我group 有人send 自稱係受害少女媽媽嘅朋友嘅錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍真on9無極限, 是鳩旦搵個大媽錄音就圍send"},{"pid":"6cd151c6e559d6e4a426c5d747d1f9652005142a","tid":1551072